{"tid":1605171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該全民同我武力升級","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:37:34.000Z","uid":308499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3bca04deff20e66735671e5632c769814466e007","tid":1605171,"uid":308499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"我係一個前線fad <br />\n係對家同自己人都可以睇到好多野<br />\n好老實咁講 其實對家928開始已經升級左好多 <br />\n你睇下琴日929就知 當時大約5點幾 一班畜聾係灣仔Mtr d2出口衝出黎 目測大約30以上畜狗 <br />\n當時係修頓附近好多都係和理非黎<br />\n佢地已經唔撚再會理你係勇武定和理非 <br />\n照㩒低 係咁扑你個頭<br />\n個時個女仔比人㩒低左 喊住咁求我地話救命<br />\n但根本幫唔到....<br />\n好撚老實講 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">火魔法已經係基本</span>[/size=5］<br />\n如果我地唔全民打狗克服心理障礙 我地真係玩撚完 輸得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日就10月1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係希望大家背熟個地圖先好同我出去發夢 <br />\n唔識路依樣野真係害死好多人<br />\n<br />\n當然 既然對家都已經升級到頂點 唔該大家都要升級咪撚再咁仁慈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f7e3e55df033b469b67969b99a72a45494b5b68","tid":1605171,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d106d3d025b28244382c72eb1ed38709f6077d5f","tid":1605171,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三點燒黨旗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［主線］<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要做啲有標誌性嘅</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604870</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理非入<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 依到有合集帶啲咩</span></strong><br />\n［整合］<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一執齊野</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">無豬咀就帶定條濕毛巾cover 口同鼻 <br />\n會好啲</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好行甘前</span>"},{"pid":"4e6fc0fc561ccbf4b6f5ff5f10d1ab4390343157","tid":1605171,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"岀po前preview下先啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日Sogo唔開 打算轉陣唔打港島⋯⋯"},{"pid":"501c97fccac31274aaec899c2e357edd26c71dc3","tid":1605171,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f6712cf2724323bc7ec3161bb834d7c7fcd5b83","tid":1605171,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"咁你fad會唔會幫手打？定救人？<br />\n<br />\n你諗諗你到閩立場好wo"},{"pid":"b812f84ade462da7bd14c3d34803f64b7a84c4a1","tid":1605171,"uid":308499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6fc0fc561ccbf4b6f5ff5f10d1ab4390343157","tid":1605171,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"岀po前preview下先啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日Sogo唔開 打算轉陣唔打港島⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"聽日其實真係遍地開花先夠打"},{"pid":"d2cbae2edabbfde27230f23a48c4f08f7821cefd","tid":1605171,"uid":308499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6712cf2724323bc7ec3161bb834d7c7fcd5b83","tid":1605171,"uid":172599,"like":0,"disl